[30;1m158 | [0m[35m  search space one by one. It crossovers the values from the parents into the[0m
[30;1m159 | [0m[35m  offspring's decision on each target point. For those points that are not[0m
[30;1m160 | [0m[35m  targeted, the decisions from the parents will be copied to the offsprings.[0m
